TITLE: Initializing Mercado Pago Client in NodeJS
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to initialize the Mercado Pago client with an access token and optional configuration.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mercadopago/sdk-nodejs.git/blob/master/README.md#2025-04-19_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
