TITLE: Installing Mercado Pago SDK for NodeJS
DESCRIPTION: Command to install the Mercado Pago SDK for NodeJS using npm.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mercadopago/sdk-nodejs.git/blob/master/README.md#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: sh
CODE:
```
$ npm install --save mercadopago
```

