TITLE: Installing Pre-commit Git Hooks in Bash
DESCRIPTION: Command to set up the git hook scripts for the SDK project after installing pre-commit. This ensures that style checks run automatically before every commit.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mercadopago/sdk-nodejs.git/blob/master/CODING_GUIDELINES.md#2025-04-19_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
$ pre-commit install
```

