TITLE: Checking Pre-commit Version in Bash
DESCRIPTION: Command to verify the installation and version of pre-commit tool, which is required for contributing to the project to check code style and formatting.
SOURCE: https://github.com/mercadopago/sdk-nodejs.git/blob/master/CODING_GUIDELINES.md#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
$ pre-commit --version
pre-commit 2.17.0
```
